---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Legal Notice - Lars Ullrich"
  description="Legal notice (Impressum) for larsullrich.de — Lars Ullrich, Berlin."
  canonical="/impressum"
>
  <main class="impressum">
    <div class="container">

      <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to home</a>

      <h1>Legal Notice</h1>

      <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <!-- § 5 DDG                                         -->
      <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section>
        <h2>Information pursuant to § 5 DDG</h2>
        <p>
          Lars Ullrich<br />
          Berlin, Germany
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <!-- Contact                                         -->
      <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Email: <a href="mailto:contact@larsullrich.de">contact@larsullrich.de</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <!-- Responsible for content — § 18 Abs. 2 MStV     -->
      <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section>
        <h2>Responsible for content pursuant to § 18 (2) MStV</h2>
        <p>
          Lars Ullrich<br />
          Berlin, Germany
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <!-- Liability                                       -->
      <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section>
        <h2>Liability for content</h2>
        <p>
          As a service provider I am responsible for my own content on these pages in accordance
          with general law pursuant to § 7 (1) TMG. Pursuant to §§ 8 to 10 TMG, however, I am
          not obliged to monitor transmitted or stored third-party information or to investigate
          circumstances that indicate illegal activity. Obligations to remove or block the use of
          information under general law remain unaffected. Liability in this regard is only possible
          from the time of knowledge of a specific infringement. Upon becoming aware of any such
          violations I will remove the relevant content immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Liability for links</h2>
        <p>
          This site contains links to external third-party websites over whose content I have no
          control. I therefore cannot accept any liability for that external content. The respective
          provider or operator of each linked page is always responsible for its content. Linked
          pages were checked for possible legal violations at the time of linking; no unlawful
          content was apparent at that time. Permanent monitoring of linked pages is not reasonable
          without concrete evidence of a violation. Upon becoming aware of any infringement I will
          remove the relevant links immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Copyright</h2>
        <p>
          The content and works on these pages created by the site operator are subject to German
          copyright law. Reproduction, editing, distribution, or any form of commercial use beyond
          the scope of copyright law requires the written consent of the respective author or
          creator. Downloads and copies of this site are permitted for private, non-commercial use
          only. Where content on this site was not created by the operator, third-party copyrights
          are respected and identified as such. If you become aware of a copyright infringement
          please contact me — upon notification I will remove the relevant content immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .impressum {
    padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem) clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 70ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--cobalt, oklch(52% 0.22 265));
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--ink, oklch(10% 0.012 258));
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--rule, oklch(87% 0.005 260));
  }

  section:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink, oklch(10% 0.012 258));
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--dim, oklch(28% 0.010 258));
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.875;
    margin: 0;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--cobalt, oklch(52% 0.22 265));
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .placeholder {
    color: var(--ghost, oklch(50% 0.006 260));
    font-style: italic;
    background: oklch(96% 0.005 260);
    padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }
</style>
